@startuml
state Unassigned {
  [*] --> Unassigned
}
state Assigned
state Unemployed
state Archived

Unassigned --> Assigned : Assign to client/campaign
Assigned --> Unassigned : Remove assignment
Assigned --> Assigned : Switch assignments
Assigned --> Unemployed : Leave job
Unemployed --> Archived : Archive after time passes
@enduml
